one_reviews_text:
Impressions Video with Commentary // Oculus Rift S // GTX 1060 (6GB):
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lAKk-QiZFBI

My Initial Impressions:
What I thought would turn out to be a terrible idea and concept, turned out to be something quite unique and special.
I really had fun with this one and can't wait to see what comes in the next in the series.

Made a video on this just search 'Gamertag VR' and 'Sharks of Mars' and it will come up.

Great graphics and such a twisted recipe works so wel. This is a small taste of what potentially could be a really great game if the developers work hard and listen to community feedback. cant wait for more
